Class InsertionServiceFieldImpl

java.lang.Object

io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.insertion.InsertionServiceFieldImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
InsertionService
public class InsertionServiceFieldImpl extends BaseInsertionService<InsertionField>
Service implementation for processing fields annotated with InsertionField.

This class inspects the InsertionField annotation on object fields, builds the appropriate Selenium By locator, determines the target ComponentType enum, and delegates to the registered insertion service to insert values into the UI component.
